measurements.description:
Five flowers on one 12-cm upright inflorescence; sepals lanceolate, 

	white marked green at the tip; petals white overlaid light purple on the edge 

	and dark purple on the distal half; lip strongly frilled at the central margin, 

	side lobes partially closed over the column, white, 

	strongly marked purple at the margins; column white mostly overlaid purple, 

	anther cap white, substance firm; texture matte.
